ek\u0026amp;#39;s Top Takes\" data-chomp-id=\"f4af4ade59f643e5a5e7e4aa3fd49eae\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-height=\"1080\" data-alt=\"Image for article titled The Biggest Surprises From The Game Awards Nominees And More Of The Week\u0026amp;#39;s Top Takes\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/f4af4ade59f643e5a5e7e4aa3fd49eae.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: GSC Game World\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"f4af4ade59f643e5a5e7e4aa3fd49eae\" data-recommend-id=\"image://f4af4ade59f643e5a5e7e4aa3fd49eae\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt was nighttime and I was creeping through grass of \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/stalker-2-devs-xbox-series-s-x-performance-60fps-mode-1851674405?_gl=1*146d5yr*_ga*MTM0Mjk0ODIxMC4xNjkxNzY3NjQ2*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczMjIyMTU0Ny40NC4xLjE3MzIyMjMyNTAuNTguMC4w\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/stalker-2-devs-xbox-series-s-x-performance-60fps-mode-1851674405?_gl=1*146d5yr*_ga*MTM0Mjk0ODIxMC4xNjkxNzY3NjQ2*_ga_V4QNJTT5L0*MTczMjIyMTU0Ny40NC4xLjE3MzIyMjMyNTAuNTguMC4w\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eS.T.A.L.K.E.R 2\u003c/em\u003e\u0026#39;\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003es digital recreation of the Chornobyl Exclusion Zone. I needed to meet up with someone, but getting anywhere in the “Zone”— the eerie, desolate, but oddly beautiful irradiated setting of the game—is dangerous. To make sure I was going the right way I pulled out my map and plotted out my next path. And then a large feral pig slammed into me out of nowhere and nearly killed me. I got up, fired a few rounds at the hog and healed, right before another pig barreled me over. - Zack Zwiezen \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/stalker-2-review-buggy-janky-impressions-xbox-pc-fps-1851705232\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/stalker-2-review-buggy-janky-impressions-xbox-pc-fps-1851705232\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
